        "title": "feat: add Firefox multi-account container support",
        "body": "Surface Firefox [Multi-Account Containers](https://support.mozilla.org/kb/containers) on each cookie so callers can tell containers apart.\n\n### Changes\n- Read `moz_cookies.originAttributes` and resolve names from the profile's `containers.json`\n- Add `Cookie.Container` (`ID` = userContextId, `Name` from containers.json; zero value = default container / non-Firefox)\n- Include the container in the dedupe key so cookies that only differ by container aren't merged\n- Add unit + integration tests\n\n### Verification\n- `make ci` (go test, golangci-lint, coverage ≥ 90%)\n- Integration test reads three containers through `Get()` and keeps them distinct",
